Your ambition is what dragged you down.

267
00:17:49,985 --> 00:17:52,571
You want an express pass to success.

268
00:17:52,738 --> 00:17:55,491
You used my husband at
the expense of my marriage!

269
00:17:56,116 --> 00:17:58,410
I trusted you. I believed in you.

270
00:17:58,619 --> 00:18:02,039
But you're the one who destroyed
whatever we started.

271
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:04,917
You did this to yourself, Helena!

272
00:18:05,626 --> 00:18:07,961
I'm giving you one last chance.

273
00:18:08,504 --> 00:18:12,716
You won't like what will happen
if you continue what you're planning.

274
00:18:13,717 --> 00:18:15,052
I'm warning you.

275
00:18:15,385 --> 00:18:16,886
[HELENA] I'm no longer afraid of you!

276
00:18:16,887 --> 00:18:18,847
Especially now that I know the truth!

277
00:18:19,056 --> 00:18:22,643
I'll kill you first before you ruin
us!

278
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:28,606
[VELMA AND HELENA GRUNT]

279
00:18:28,607 --> 00:18:29,607
[HELENA COUGHS]

280
00:18:49,169 --> 00:18:50,545
[VELMA] Get up here!

281
00:18:50,546 --> 00:18:52,816
- [VELMA] Come here and shut your mouth!
- [HELENA] Don't touch me!

282
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,966
[HELENA] Let go of me!

283
00:18:55,592 --> 00:18:57,886
I will fight you until death!

284
00:18:59,763 --> 00:19:00,763
[HELENA GASPS]

285
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:06,061
Just remember that nobody
wins against Velma Imperial.

286
00:19:07,855 --> 00:19:10,274
[KRISELDA] He's the one who pushed her.

287
00:19:11,316 --> 00:19:12,985
All my gut feelings were right!

288
00:19:14,528 --> 00:19:17,906
But why are you just saying and
showing me these things now?

289
00:19:17,948 --> 00:19:19,428
You should have shown me this before!

290
00:19:19,533 --> 00:19:23,203
Noreen, all of that information
is new to me too.

291
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:27,290
This is new?

292
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:30,460
Why are you helping me to continue this?

293
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:38,135
What do you want in return,
after dropping all those truths on me?

294
00:19:41,054 --> 00:19:43,015
Because there's a deeper reason.
